---
const {
    class: classProp
} = Astro.props

//If you want to change the responsive height of footer:
//tweak the `[--footer-height:${x}]` classes inside of footer component
---

<footer class:list={[
    classProp,
    "[--footer-height:8] h-[calc(var(--block-size)*var(--footer-height))] xs:[--footer-height:7] sm:[--footer-height:6] md:[--footer-height:4] w-full bg-block-bedrock"
]}>
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between h-full p-5 bg-dark-75 text-white">
        <header class="flex flex-col w-full sm:w-[60%]">
            <img src="/imgs/logo.png" class="h-full max-w-[20ch] m-[-10px]" />
            <br/>
            <p class="text-2xl">竹像素 | BambooPixel</p>
            <p class="text-sm">我们致力于打造一个公平、友好、和谐的游戏环境，让每一位玩家都能享受到游戏带来的乐趣与成就感。但请记得，这需要我们共同的努力与维护。请时刻以开放的心态、尊重的态度对待每一位游戏伙伴，共同营造一个积极向上、充满正能量的游戏社区。
            </p>
        </header>
        <nav class="self-end flex flex-col items-end gap-1 text-link">
            <a href="https://github.com/BryceRussell/astro-minecraft-theme" class="link">Download</a>
            <a href="https://github.com/BryceRussell" class="link">Github</a>
            <a href="https://astro.build" class="link">Astro</a>
            <a href="https://discord.com/invite/grF4GTXXYm" class="link">Discord</a>
        </nav>
    </div>
</footer>
